---
By: David Seabury
Locus:
  Page: 417
  Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Selfishness
---
Little souls wish you to be unhappy. It aggravates them to have you joyous,
efficient and free. ...It gives their egos wings if yours are clipped. You
can ruin your life in an hour by listening to their puerile opinions.
